6 February 2008Government will hold parliamentary media briefings in Cape Town, from 11 - 15 February 2008. This will be the first cycle of media briefings for the year.The briefings will take place at Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.The briefing schedule:- NB: International Relations, Peace and Security Cluster briefing, and 2010 Soccer World Cup briefing to be confirmed -Enquiries Colin Cruywagen Cell: 082 377 9916Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)